      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, you\u2019d think this beauty just rolled off the showroom floor today\u2014it\u2019s that clean! It's been pampered since day one, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and there isn't a single scratch or smudge to be found. It drives like a total dream and still has that wonderful new-car smell. I'm really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall head over heels for it! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a peek!",
