    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering a concours-standard 997.2 Carrera S, featuring the 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six paired with a rare 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen exhibits peak mechanical health with a clean over-rev report and zero bore scoring. Performance is enhanced by the Sport Chrono Package and Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), providing precise damping and sharpened throttle response. The drivetrain includes a mechanical locking rear differential for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis is rigid and rattle-free, while the braking system utilizes four-piston aluminum monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors for consistent thermal management. Meticulously detailed with an unblemished underbody and factory-fresh paint depth, this is a turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
