      "description": "This FD3S chassis is a superlative example of 90s JDM engineering, featuring a meticulously maintained 13B-REW rotary powerplant with factory-spec sequential turbocharging. The apex seals maintain optimal compression, ensuring the high-revving power delivery remains linear and responsive across the entire tachometer. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise short-throw five-speed manual and a Torsen limited-slip differential, providing exceptional torque distribution under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry is factory-perfect, utilizing aluminum double-wishbones at all four corners for uncompromising kinematic precision. With a flawless undercarriage and zero vacuum leak issues in the complex 'rat's nest' control system, this unit represents a turn-key investment for the serious purist.",
